V0208_01_00_00_0.text: You'll plummet into the shadowy depths of the Netherworld!

V0208_01_00_00_1.text: At the hands of my Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_01_00_01_0.text: Do you have a strategy to counter my handless combo?

V0208_01_00_02_0.text: Get ready for the Duel of your life! Literally!

V0208_01_00_03_1.text: Get fired up or burn down into ash!

V0208_01_00_04_0.text: You don’t know how long I’ve been waiting for my revenge.

V0208_01_00_04_1.text:
It’s a shame it’ll be over so quickly.
Hahahahaha!

V0208_01_00_05_0.text: Is it time for The Enforcers to ride again?

V0208_01_00_06_0.text: I was once your friend, but I'm now your enemy!

V0208_01_00_06_1.text: And I'm back to unleash my wrath on this birdbrain!

V0208_01_00_07_0.text: Let the war between the Signers and Dark Signers begin!

V0208_03_00_01_0.text: Nothing you play will save you from my wrath!

V0208_03_00_02_0.text: Let's enjoy tearing each other to shreds!

V0208_03_00_05_0.text:
Mark my words!
You’ll pay for this!

V0208_05_00_00_0.text: My handless combo will shake you to your core!

V0208_06_01_00_0.text: You can't get that by me!

V0208_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0208_08_00_00_0.text: I have no cards in my hand, so I can activate ZERO-MAX!

V0208_08_00_01_0.text: I activate my Continuous Spell, Infernity Launcher!

V0208_08_00_03_0.text: My hand's empty, so I can use my Launcher's other effect!

V0208_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Into the Void!

V0208_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Continuous Spell, Wave-Motion Inferno!

V0208_08_00_06_0.text: I use Wave-Motion Inferno to send my hand to the Graveyard!

V0208_08_00_07_0.text:
Hahahaha!
This card will resurrect my Immortal!

V0208_08_00_08_0.text: Your lame tricks won't work against my Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Infernity Inferno!

V0208_08_00_12_0.text:
Don't mock my handless combo!
Go, Infernity Force!

V0208_08_00_13_0.text:
Witness my handless combo!
I activate Infernity Break!

V0208_08_00_14_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Infernity Reflector!

V0208_08_00_15_1.text:
...Just kidding!
I activate my Trap, Damage Translation!

V0208_08_00_16_0.text: During the End Phase, Damage Translation's other effect!

V0208_08_00_16_1.text: I create a Ghost Token for every time I take effect damage!

V0208_08_00_17_0.text:
I knew you'd do that!
My Continuous Trap, Depth Amulet!

V0208_08_00_18_0.text:
I discard a card to activate Depth Amulet!
You can't attack!

V0208_08_00_20_0.text:
My handless combo begins!
My Continuous Trap, Phantom Hand!

V0208_08_00_21_0.text:
Phantom Hand's effect activates!
My hand will be empty!

V0208_08_00_22_0.text:
I flip over my Trap Card!
Limit Impulse!

V0208_08_00_22_1.text: I send two cards to the Graveyard to summon two Soul Tokens!

V0208_08_00_23_0.text:
My Counter Trap activates!
Infernity Barrier!

V0208_08_00_24_1.text: I activate my Trap, Offering to the Immortals!

V0208_08_00_25_0.text: That won't work against an Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_08_00_25_1.text: I activate my Counter Trap, Earthbound Wave!

V0208_08_00_26_0.text: Never mess with an Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_08_00_26_1.text: The Continuous Trap, Roar of the Earthbound!

V0208_08_00_27_0.text:
Are you nuts?
Roar of the Earthbound's effect activates!

V0208_08_00_28_0.text:
Heh... Fine!
I'll resurrect my Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_08_00_28_1.text:
I activate my Trap!
Revival of the Immortals!

V0208_08_00_29_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Altar of the Bound Deity!

V0208_08_00_30_0.text: Altar of the Bound Deity's effect activates!

V0208_08_00_32_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Passion of Baimasse!

V0208_09_00_00_0.text: Since I have no hand, Infernity General's effect activates!

V0208_09_00_01_0.text: I can Special Summon this card by showing it to you!

V0208_09_00_02_0.text: And Infernity Archfiend's effect adds a card to my hand!

V0208_09_00_03_0.text: My hand's empty, so take Infernity Destroyer's effect!

V0208_09_00_05_0.text: When Necromancer is summoned, it switches to defense!

V0208_09_00_06_0.text: My hand is empty, so I can activate Necromancer's effect!

V0208_09_00_08_0.text: My hand's empty, so Infernity Mirage's effect activates!

V0208_09_00_09_0.text: Infernity Avenger's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0208_09_00_11_0.text: I activate Hundred Eyes Dragon's effect!

V0208_09_00_11_1.text: It banishes a Dark Monster from my Grave to gain its effect!

V0208_09_00_12_1.text: By destroying my dragon, I get the Dark Signers' ace card!

V0208_09_00_13_0.text: You thought your monster protected you, but you were wrong!

V0208_09_00_13_1.text: Ccapac Apu deals damage equal to your monster's ATK!

V0208_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0208_13_00_07_0.text:
Heh heh heh...
Rise, Infernity Necromancer!

V0208_13_00_14_0.text: Vorse Raider will get my revenge!

V0208_37_00_00_0.text: When the shadows are devoured by even darker shadows...

V0208_37_00_00_1.text:
A world without light is revealed!
Dark Synchro!

V0208_13_00_15_0.text:
The shadow of the Netherworld! 
Hundred Eyes Dragon!

V0208_13_00_17_0.text: Give strength to my Immortal, Earthbound Linewalker!

V0208_14_00_00_0.text:
Let's battle!
But don't surrender too quickly!

V0208_16_00_00_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Time for the big finale!

V0208_16_00_01_0.text: Prepare to meet the shadows because this is game over!

V0208_19_00_16_0.text: Join the rest of the taken in the Netherworld!

V0208_19_00_16_1.text:
Ccapac Apu!
Pound this pathetic peon into the darkness!

V0208_21_00_00_0.text:
I'm surprised you survived.
But will you next turn?

V0208_21_00_01_0.text: I won't let you off the hook that easily.

V0208_28_00_00_1.text: Not the childish games you were playing!

V0208_28_00_01_0.text: I'll let you go for now.

V0208_28_00_01_1.text: But you must live with the fact that you cried in terror!

V0208_28_00_02_1.text: Not enough to douse my fire for revenge!

V0208_28_00_03_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Beg me not to send you to the Netherworld!

V0208_28_00_04_0.text:
My dear old friend Yusei!
You're finished!

V0208_28_00_04_1.text: After what you did to me, this is sweet justice!

V0208_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh!
I will crush you in our rematch!

V0208_29_00_01_0.text: Seems you're willing to do anything to survive.

V0208_29_00_02_0.text: Grr! This doesn't quench my thirst for revenge!

V0208_29_00_03_0.text: This was not a satisfying ending.

V0208_33_00_01_0.text: Feel the sheer terror of my Earthbound Immortal!

V0208_34_00_00_0.text: This is what my handless combo can do!

V0208_34_00_02_0.text: Trust me when I say the worst is yet to come.

V0208_34_00_03_0.text: I will sacrifice you to Ccapac Apu!

V0208_34_00_05_0.text: This is the final Duel for The Enforcers!

V0208_34_00_08_0.text: That's not enough to satisfy me.

V0208_35_00_00_0.text:
Satisfy my thirst for revenge!
Hahahaha!

V0208_35_00_01_0.text: The clash between the Signers and Dark Signers begins!

V0208_27_00_02_0.text: I've had enough of your tricks!
